USE hahn; $formatDate = DateTime::Format("%Y-%m-%d");

SELECT
    CAST(null as Int64) as msku,
    CAST(null as Int64) as warehouse_id,
    CAST(null as Int64) as supplier_id,
    CAST(null as Int64) as category_id,
    `date`,
    sum(item_count) as sales,
    avg(item_count) as avg_sales,
    sum(cast(sales.item_price_rub_numeric as double)) as price,
    avg(cast(sales.item_price_rub_numeric as double)) as avg_price
FROM RANGE (
`/home/market/production/mstat/analyst/regular/cubes_vertica/fact_new_order_item_dict`,
'2021-12',
'2021-12'
)  with inline   as sales
JOIN `/home/market/production/mstat/analyst/regular/cubes_vertica/fact_new_order_dict`  with inline as orders
    ON sales.order_id = orders.id
LEFT JOIN `/home/market/production/mstat/analyst/regular/cubes_vertica/fact_new_order_delivery`  with inline as deliveries
    ON sales.order_id = deliveries.order_id
LEFT JOIN `/home/market/production/mstat/dictionaries/mbo/sku_transitions/latest`  with inline as sku_transitions
    ON sales.market_sku = sku_transitions.old_entity_id
WHERE orders.market_fulfilment_flag AND sales.warehouse_id IS NOT NULL
    AND LENGTH(sales.real_supplier_id) > 0 AND (deliveries.shipment_datetime > '1970-01-01T00:00:00'
    OR (orders.order_status != 'CANCELLED' AND orders.order_status != 'CANCELLED_WITHOUT_REFUND'))
    AND DateTime::MakeDate(DateTime::ParseIso8601(orders.creation_date))
    BETWEEN Date('2021-12-13') AND Date('2021-12-27')
    
    
     AND sales.partner_id in (777) 
    
    
GROUP BY
            $formatDate(DateTime::StartOfWeek(DateTime::ParseIso8601(orders.creation_date)))
    as `date`
ORDER BY `date`
